Dug Dug Folding Seat for Royal Enfield Bullet Standard 350 Electra 350 – Black
Description:
Folding Seat for Royal Enfield
Dug Dug presents all-new Heavy Quality Folding Seat for Royal Enfield Standard 350 Electra 350 all Models. Dug Dug Folding Seat is contoured to fit the rider’s body shape. This design helps distribute the rider’s weight evenly, reducing pressure points and discomfort during long rides. Made from premium quality material. 
The type and quality of padding used in our Foldable Seat greatly impacts comfort. Our High-density foam provides support and helps reduce vibrations and absorb shocks. The width of the seat plays a role in rider comfort. Our wider seat can provide more room for the rider to move around, while other narrower seats can discomfort the rider. Rear Seat Load Capacity: Up To 100kg. 
The fabric used in our foldable seat and the stitching pattern affects both aesthetics and comfort. Our seats feature double stitching for added durability. Dug Dug Foldable Seat with sufficient padding for passengers is essential for a comfortable two-up riding experience and once ride is done you can hide Rear Seat When Not In Use.
